    public class DivWidget
extends FlowPanel
implements HasStyle, IsResponsive, HasId
    A simple div widget with support for child widgets.

    UiBinder Usage:

     <b:DivWidget>
     <b:SomeChildWidget />
     <b:AnotherChildWidget />
 </b:DivWidget>

    Since:
    2.0.4.0
    Author:
    Carlos Alexandro Becker, Dominik Mayer
